{"tid":630669,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西布朗勢降班 盧卡古：心如刀割","createTime":"2018-04-15T19:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T04:40:25.000Z","uid":112702,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6385f27aeefcc0911b1d2acf004442bcf93c42","tid":630669,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T19:09:57.000Z","msg":"周日英超，紅魔曼聯主場迎戰榜尾的西布朗，中鋒盧卡古為前東家的狀況坦言感到心如刀割。<br />\n<br />\n比利時國腳盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）曾在2012/13球季效力西布朗，英超上陣35場射入17球，表現出色，令他獲多支勁旅招手，輾轉間今季以7500萬鎊由愛華頓改投曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n剩下5輪，前東家西布朗距離安全線多達10分，恐怕劫數難逃，周日倒戈的盧卡古賽前表示：「對我而言，這場比賽心如刀割，其中幾名西布朗球員是我的朋友，看到他們排在榜尾，心情也不好受。」<br />\n<br />\n該名24歲中鋒坦言：「退一步海闊天空，有時候我們把教訓當作上堂，學到東西，改善自己。我不希望他們降班，希望他們也能從中汲取教訓，藉此準備新球季。其實，我不清楚西布朗的問題所在，我只是翻看比賽精華，也很難了解箇中到底發生了甚麼，希望他們找回成功之匙。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d79ba9ab47982fc715a3a8249d96bda87c91dc","tid":630669,"uid":88442,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T19:11:06.000Z","msg":"行動證明一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f569dd84cd1d23e19d31b7ddb8d3585a51d249","tid":630669,"uid":131526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"59df5759d8093b855c0155e71f67957b96a4adf5","tid":630669,"uid":64689,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:17:51.000Z","msg":"義犬執恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed841d3da9703a8fb240461afae3ed2aa2765836","tid":630669,"uid":64689,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"59df5759d8093b855c0155e71f67957b96a4adf5","tid":630669,"uid":64689,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:17:51.000Z","msg":"義犬執恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T23:18:23.000Z","msg":"報<sp